Combine crumbs and butter; press on bottom and up side to rim of lightly buttered 9-inch pie plate. Chill. In large mixing bowl, beat chocolate with EAGLE BRAND(R) and vanilla until well blended. Chill 10 to 15 minutes. Fold in whipped cream. Pour into prepared crust. Freeze 6 hours or until firm. Garnish as desired. Freeze leftovers.